{
  "stem": "22869.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it's an interesting question, because as I mentioned before, we were not really in a-- in a classification what you'd call a middle class, or a solid middle class family.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When Hitler occupied Poland, the Nazis-- or the-- I should say the German soldiers-- needed food and-- and they needed wine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have to tell you, on the fronts, they tried to give the soldiers the best they can.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some German officers would come in, in our city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember the first time when they walked in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was on a Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They walked into my father's house, and they were very polite.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told my father that they would like to buy some wine that they need for the soldiers on the front in Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not occupied yet, at that time, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm talking about '39, '40.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father told them, I'm sorry, I cannot deal with you today, it's the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and-- and no matter how much money you want to spend, there's no doubt about it that I will not even discuss it with you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you're willing to wait till the evening, when the Sabbath is over, then we can talk business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they excused themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were very polite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I can remember this like today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were from the Wehrmacht, you know, the regular army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they came back in the evening, and-- and I recall very vividly that they came in with some briefcases.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They bought our whole wine cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, every little bit that was there, lock, stock, and barrel, so to say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took out their-- opened up their suitcases, and they had brand-new, printed Slovakian money.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
